value: Le livre à partient à Pierre Biller Bon garcon, ?17th c. (pen-trial, fol. 155v); A. Brölemann (heraldic bookplate, inside upper cover); sale-room(?) sticker with 'Ni. 504' and 'A. 221' (in different hands), 19th / 20th c. (inside upper cover); Mme Etienne Mallet; her sale, Sotheby's, 4 May 1926, lot 73; gift of Mrs May Cippico, in accordance with the wishes of Mrs Constance Goetze, 19 April 1951.
